<paragraph id="IFRS16_56" base="F45929399"><paranum>56</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 16"/><data name="paranum" value="56"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS16_P0211">If <xref base="F45929827" href="IFRS16_APPA.dita#IFRS16_APPA/IFRS16_P0388">right-of-use assets<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0342"/></ph></xref> meet the definition of investment property, a <xref base="F45929736" href="IFRS16_APPA.dita#IFRS16_APPA/IFRS16_P0380">lessee<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0220"/></ph></xref> shall apply the disclosure requirements in <xref id="IFRS16_X0246" base="F47961025" href="../ias40/IAS40_TOC0001.dita#IAS40_TOC0001/IAS40_TOC0001_V4">IAS 40</xref>. In that case, a lessee is not required to provide the disclosures in <xref id="IFRS16_X0247" base="F47961026" href="IFRS16_53.dita#IFRS16_53">paragraph 53(a), (f), (h) or (j)</xref> for those right-of-use assets.</p></body></paragraph>